671
01:13:25,819 --> 01:13:37,668
truly inclusive in whatever policy ends up being created, that it represents all of our learners here within the district.

672
01:13:39,189 --> 01:13:39,569
Thank you.

673
01:13:40,149 --> 01:13:43,892
Thank you.

